      • createChunkHeader

        public static ChunkHeader createChunkHeader(int documentVersion,
                                            byte[] data,
                                            int offset)
        Creates the appropriate ChunkHeader for the Chunk Header at the given location, for the given document version.(为给定文档版本的给定位置的块标头创建适当的块标头。)
        Parameters:
        documentVersion - the documentVersion - 4 and higher is supported(documentVersion -支持documentVersion - 4及更高版本)
        data - the chunk data(数据-块数据)
        offset - the start offset in the chunk data(偏离-块数据中的开始偏离)
        Returns:
        the ChunkHeader(ChunkHeader)
